struct  MM_LoadDumpFileHeader_t
 MM Load and Dump file header structure We use the same header structure for both dump and load files so a dump file can be reloaded back into memory if desired (providing a memory save and restore capability). This MM header is the secondary header, the standard cFE file header is primary header for all load and dump files. More...
